Usage: set_min_pulse_width [-help] <value> [<object_list>] [-high] [-low]
                           [-waveform_aware_type {absolute source_width_ratio}]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<value>                   # Specifies minimum pulse width check value
                          # (float, required)
<object_list>             # List of objects: pins, ports or clocks
                          # (string, optional)
-high                     # Specifies for high min pulse width (bool, optional)
-low                      # Specifies for low min pulse width (bool, optional)
-waveform_aware_type {absolute source_width_ratio}
                          # waveform aware pulse width check to apply value as
                          # absolute or source_width_ratio (enum, optional)